**Kasm hardware requirements**
CPU - 2 cores
Memory - 4GB
Storage - min 50GB (SSD)

# Single-Server install guide: https://www.kasmweb.com/docs/latest/install/single_server_install.html
# Find the latest release: https://www.kasmweb.com/docs/latest/release_notes.html

# Pre-install:
# 1. Ensure your system is up-to-date with the latest patches and updates
# 2. Install Docker Compose: https://github.com/FullerFi/self-host/blob/main/Docker/docker_compose_install

# Initial install:
# 1. Download the latest version to /tmp

cd /tmp
curl -O https://kasm-static-content.s3.amazonaws.com/kasm_release_1.16.1.98d6fa.tar.gz
tar -xf kasm_release_1.16.1.98d6fa.tar.gz
sudo bash kasm_release/install.sh

# *** Make sure to SAVE THE CREDENTIALS at the end of the login process ***

# Navigate to https://<kasm_server_ip_addy>
# Log in with the 'admin@kasm.local' creds
